videos.headline: Boise State's Rypien connects with Wilson
videos.description: Brett Rypien finds an open Cedrick Wilson for a 22-yard pass on a drive that would result in a Broncos' field goal.

videos.headline: Fresno State's McMaryion rushes for TD
videos.description: Seeing no one open, Fresno State QB Marcus McMaryion runs for a 1-yard touchdown to take the lead over the Broncos.

videos.headline: Boise State's Mattison muscles into end zone
videos.description: Alexander Mattison pushes his way through the pile for a 3-yard touchdown for the Broncos.

videos.headline: Fresno State's McMaryion scores second TD
videos.description: Marcus McMaryion finds a gap in the defense and runs 8 yards for a Bulldogs' touchdown, his second of the quarter.

videos.headline: Boise State's Wolpin bursts into end zone
videos.description: Ryan Wolpin finds a gap and runs 2 yards for a touchdown to give the Broncos the lead in the final minutes of the 4th quarter.
